        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1750475766" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8570039048519630320">Amazingly prescient book. Written in the late 1990s and it&apos;s incredible how much of what Barber describes has come to pass. He does a great job describing the fundamental forces driving so much of the conflict we see in the world today and, unlike most of the articles you&apos;ll read, actually attempts to describe how we can come to resolution.</span>
  <span id="freeText8570039048519630320" style="display:none">Amazingly prescient book. Written in the late 1990s and it's incredible how much of what Barber describes has come to pass. He does a great job describing the fundamental forces driving so much of the conflict we see in the world today and, unlike most of the articles you'll read, actually attempts to describe how we can come to resolution.</span>
  <a data-text-id="8570039048519630320" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


